-- China Longyuan Rated `Buy' in New Coverage at BNP Paribas on Wind Power
-- Shiyin Chen
-- 2010-06-13T23:13:30Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-13/china-longyuan-rated-buy-in-new-coverage-at-bnp-paribas-on-wind-power.html

          
          
             China Longyuan Power Group Corp. was
rated “buy” in new coverage by BNP Paribas analysts Daisy
Zhang and Simon Hao, who said the company is “one of the best
ways” to invest in the growth of wind power capacity in China.  
 The analysts have a share-price estimate of HK$10.88.  
